## 3. Typography & Layout System

### 3.1 Typeface Selection
* **Display & Headings:** `Public Sans` (or fallback standard Sans-Serif system stack).
* **Body & UI Elements:** `Inter` (or fallback Sans-Serif).
* **Technical Data, System Logs, & Code:** `IBM Plex Mono` (or standard system Monospace).

### 3.2 Scales & Hierarchy Rules
Avoid setting font sizes in pixels (`px`). Use scale-relative `rem` values based on a default 100% root size.

```css
html {
  font-size: 100%; /* Respects user-agent zoom preferences */
}
body {
  font-size: 1.0625rem; /* ~17px base size */
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
}
```

